ASSET SOURCES
-------------
- Pokemon sprites sourced from:
  * PokeAPI (https://github.com/PokeAPI/sprites) distributed under CC0 1.0 Universal License.
  * Pokémon Showdown / Smogon Sprite Project (https://github.com/smogon/pokemon-showdown).
